<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:13:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>甘茨辞职后内塔尼亚胡解散以色列战时内阁，本格维尔要求纳入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dissolves-war-cabinet-after-gantz-exit-ben-gvir-demands-for-inclusion/00000190-25b6-d2de-af9e-65f6ad120000</link><description>一位政治消息人士称，解散内阁严格来说是声明性的，旨在防止极右翼部长参与敏感决策；战时内阁最初是在中间派议员甘茨和艾森科特于十月加入内塔尼亚胡战时政府时组建的</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:06:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dissolves-war-cabinet-after-gantz-exit-ben-gvir-demands-for-inclusion/00000190-25b6-d2de-af9e-65f6ad120000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡支持以色列国防军10月7日的“背叛”阴谋，指责以色列最高法院“掩盖真相”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/yair-netanyahu-bolsters-idf-oct-7-betrayal-conspiracy-accuses-top-court-of-cover-up/00000190-2548-df6a-a3f6-2f5810440000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列总理之子猛烈抨击了高等法院暂停国家监察机构对军队行动调查的决定，并暗示法院希望成立一个“左翼掩盖委员会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/yair-netanyahu-bolsters-idf-oct-7-betrayal-conspiracy-accuses-top-court-of-cover-up/00000190-2548-df6a-a3f6-2f5810440000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级特使访问该地区，白宫试图阻止以色列与真主党全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-special-envoy-to-visit-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-lebanon-escalation/00000190-2237-d4b4-a7d6-eaf791520000</link><description>尽管拜登政府在霍赫斯坦的会谈中表达了紧迫性，但高级官员承认，加沙战争的结束和人质的释放是在以色列和黎巴嫩边境达成协议的必要条件</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-special-envoy-to-visit-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-lebanon-escalation/00000190-2237-d4b4-a7d6-eaf791520000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列在黎巴嫩袭击车辆；哈马斯卫生部称10名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-live/israeli-military-says-hezbollah-bringing-us-to-brink-of-escalation/00000190-2411-df11-a3b9-a5174e600000</link><description>以色列军方发言人称真主党“将我们带到了升级的边缘” ■ 以色列国防军表示，在以色列北部阿卡附近拦截了来自黎巴嫩的空中目标 ■ 以色列国防军宣布每日“战术暂停”，试图增加对加沙的援助流量 ■ 反对政府封锁的抗议者以色列的主要高速公路</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-live/israeli-military-says-hezbollah-bringing-us-to-brink-of-escalation/00000190-2411-df11-a3b9-a5174e600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方非法拘留11名反政府抗议者近一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</link><description>周日早上，警方提出了限制释放抗议者的请求，但到下午，只有三人按照法律要求被带去参加第一次保释听证会。被捕并随后被释放的人包括《国土报》摄影师伊泰·罗恩 (Itai Ron)</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 21:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列联盟重新提出有争议的法案，赋予政府对城市拉比任命的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</link><description>由于联盟成员之间存在分歧，该法案的讨论于三月份暂停，随后将恢复讨论。该法案还允许政府任命并资助约 600 名新拉比</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院规定，父亲在出生后皈依基督教的孩子可能会获得以色列公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</link><description>Ronnen 和 Vogelman 法官表示，授予身份符合《公民法》保护家庭单位和确保儿童福利的客观目的</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府组织向内塔尼亚胡联盟发起“抵抗周”，要求达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</link><description>经过动荡的一周后，三个抗议团体正在为为期一周的全国性抗议和封锁做准备，呼吁所有以色列人立即加入他们的选举要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在西岸袭击巴勒斯坦牧羊人和以色列活动人士</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</link><description>活动人士称，定居者曾两次殴打他们以及他们正在帮助的牧羊人，并向他们投掷石块</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会小组推动将预备役军人豁免年龄延长一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</link><description>规范该措施的紧急命令将于六月底到期，即生效四个月后。如果议会通过该提案，士兵将在预备役服役至41岁，军官将服役至46岁，担任关键职务的预备役人员将服役至50岁</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前议员在讨论加沙战争时引用希特勒的话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/former-israeli-mk-quotes-hitler-while-discussing-gaza-war/00000190-224f-d231-a1b2-e65f76fe0000</link><description>摩西·费林 (Moshe Feiglin) 对第 12 频道新闻说：“正如希特勒所说，如果只剩下一名犹太人，我就无法生存”，如果加沙还剩下一名“伊斯兰纳粹分子”，我们就无法生活在这里。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:52:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/former-israeli-mk-quotes-hitler-while-discussing-gaza-war/00000190-224f-d231-a1b2-e65f76fe0000</guid></item><item><title>一名新的民警正在记录以色列反政府抗议活动中警察的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-civilian-guard-is-documenting-police-brutality-at-israels-anti-government-protests/00000190-2134-d880-a7f5-b5f4d8f40000</link><description>Magen Ezrachi（又称“平民盾牌”）让志愿者到现场记录抗议活动中的虐待行为，在本-格维尔的统治下，以色列警察一直对示威者、记者甚至在加沙被扣押的人质家人使用武力。一名志愿者说：“我不应该害怕保护我的执法组织”</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-civilian-guard-is-documenting-police-brutality-at-israels-anti-government-protests/00000190-2134-d880-a7f5-b5f4d8f40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对遵守犹太安息日的愤世嫉俗的规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-16/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-cynical-rules-for-observing-the-jewish-sabbath/00000190-21dd-dee3-af9b-e7dd60010000</link><description>以色列总理通常不会在周六犹太安息日期间发布公开信息。自加沙战争爆发以来，内塔尼亚胡已经两次打破了它，这完美地解释了他无与伦比的政治犬儒主义</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 17:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-16/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-cynical-rules-for-observing-the-jewish-sabbath/00000190-21dd-dee3-af9b-e7dd60010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 254 天：以色列国防军否认内塔尼亚胡不知道拉法暂停的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-254-idf-rejects-claim-netanyahu-didnt-know-about-pauses-in-rafah/00000190-21ef-df11-a3b9-a1ef364a0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布每天在拉法进行“战术暂停”，以便向加沙提供更多援助 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特声称他们不知道这一决定 ■ 以色列最高法院于 10 月 7 日下令停止国家审计长对国防机构失败的调查 ■ 哈马斯政治局局长哈尼亚表示，该组织对当前停战提案的回应符合拜登提出的原则 ■ 这是战争开始 254 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 16:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-254-idf-rejects-claim-netanyahu-didnt-know-about-pauses-in-rafah/00000190-21ef-df11-a3b9-a1ef364a0000</guid></item><item><title>和平企业家毛兹·伊农 (Maoz Inon) 在拿撒勒这座“希望悬崖上的城市”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</link><description>2020 年，随着 COVID-19 大流行的肆虐，伊农开始了他的拿撒勒之旅。现在，10 月 7 日他的父母在以色列南部被哈马斯杀害后，他向参与者讲述了“创造希望”的行为以及旅游业作为共存力量的故事</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:49:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院叫停国家审计长对以色列国防军辛贝特 10 月 7 日失败的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</link><description>吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨法官以“复杂的安全局势”为由解释了法院的决定，并补充说，推迟调查的决定也是根据国防官员向法院提交的机密声明而做出的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布每日“战术暂停”加沙战斗，以允许援助物资进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡总理办公室否认总理了解这一政策，但军方官员表示，这符合他的命令。与国防部长加兰特关系密切的消息人士称，他并不了解军队的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</guid></item><item><title>“课堂内外的以色列和巴勒斯坦话语有多么不同，令人震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人对哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的支持表明了他们与以色列人的共同点：绝望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</link><description>一项针对加沙和西岸巴勒斯坦人的最新民意调查显示，八个月的流血和破坏并没有削弱人们对哈马斯及其 10 月 7 日袭击的支持。对于以色列人、巴勒斯坦人和国际社会来说，其结果表明为什么冲突的新解决方案如此迫切</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚特别工作组全面揭露了自 10 月 7 日以来校园内学生和教师的反犹太主义行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</link><description>教授的反犹太主义言论、对犹太学生的骚扰——哥伦比亚大学反犹太主义工作组自 11 月成立以来已听取了数百份证词。其成员向《国土报》讲述了他们计划的强制方向，并表示他们已经就反犹太主义的“教育”定义达成一致。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>